projectGridLines.title: Title: Design validation of IC,   Project 2 Title: Mixed Signal IC design
projectGridLines.description:
Title: Design validation of IC

Description: Measurement of IC parameters across temperature and supply

Skill sets: Coding(Python), some mixed signal design

Expected learning: Lab equipment and usage, measurement techniques

Specific courses required for project execution: Analog design, Digital design


Project 2 Title: Mixed Signal IC design


Description: Design of mixed signal circuits (new or improvement of existing designs)

Skill sets: Mixed signal design

Expected learning: Understand mixed signal circuit and the system in which the circuit

operates

Specific courses required for project execution: Analog Design
